---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Digital Transformation" description="End-to-end transformation for B2B, B2C, and government clients — from process diagnosis to live systems your team operates independently.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(160deg,#03142E 0%,#010A18 100%);padding:48px 24px 40px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.1);">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Digital Transformation</div>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(22px,6vw,36px);letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:10px;">From Spreadsheets<br><em style="font-style:normal;color:var(--gold);">to Systems That Scale.</em></h1>
    <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.6;max-width:460px;margin:0 auto 28px;">End-to-end transformation for B2B, B2C, and government clients — we diagnose, design, build, and transfer. Your team owns the outcome.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;min-width:220px;">Book a Discovery Call</a>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">The Problem</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Most transformation projects fail at handoff</h2>
    <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:16px;">The pattern is predictable: a consulting firm delivers a strategy deck, a software vendor delivers a system, and three months later the team is still running the old process in parallel because nothing was designed for how the work actually gets done.</p>
    <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">Transformation that sticks requires three things working together: a realistic diagnosis of current-state operations, systems designed around the actual workflow (not the ideal one), and a team trained to own what's been built. That's what we deliver.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">How It Works</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Four stages, one outcome</h2>

    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:28px;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(215,161,61,0.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);">1</div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:4px;">Digital Maturity Assessment</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">We map current-state operations across people, process, and technology. We identify where the gaps are, what the cost of staying put is, and what a realistic transition looks like — including what your team can actually absorb.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:28px;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(215,161,61,0.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);">2</div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:4px;">Transformation Roadmap</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">A sequenced implementation plan with clear ownership, realistic timelines, and measurable milestones. No 200-page strategy decks — a working document the team can execute against.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:28px;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(215,161,61,0.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);">3</div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:4px;">Build &amp; Integration</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">We build the systems — AI tools, workflow automations, digital platforms — and integrate them into your existing environment. Everything is tested in production conditions before handoff.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(215,161,61,0.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);">4</div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:4px;">Team Transfer &amp; Optimization</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">Training, documentation, and a 90-day stabilization window where we're available to optimize as the team learns. The goal: your team owns it independently. No perpetual consulting dependency.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Markets -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Markets We Serve</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">B2B · B2C · B2G</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;gap:12px;">
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:18px;">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:6px;">B2B — Wholesale &amp; Distribution</div>
        <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin:0;">ERP modernization, order automation, supplier portal digitization. Particularly for distributors and operators dealing with complex multi-market supply chains.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:18px;">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:6px;">B2C — E-commerce &amp; Retail</div>
        <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin:0;">Customer experience automation, omnichannel integration, AI-driven merchandising, and CRM transformation for consumer-facing operations.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:18px;">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:6px;">B2G — Government &amp; Public Sector</div>
        <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin:0;">Service delivery digitization, process standardization, and citizen-facing AI systems for government agencies pursuing digital-first operations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(215,161,61,0.08) 0%,rgba(3,20,46,0.6) 100%);border-top:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.15);padding:40px 24px;text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:20px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.3;">Start with the assessment</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:24px;">30 minutes to map where you are and what a realistic path forward looks like.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;min-width:220px;">Book a Discovery Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
